text: George Gibbs (3 October 1905 – 27 February 1987) was a former Australian rules footballer who played with Fitzroy and Collingwood in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * *George Gibbs's profile at Collingwood Forever Category:1905 births Category:1987 deaths Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Fitzroy Football Club players Category:Collingwood Football Club players
